In this course, you will learn how to use a Jupyter notebook. and you will be taught how to run a jupyter notebook locally using anaconda and remotely using the cloud base jupyter notebook Google colab.

You will also be exposed to the basics of python. Concepts like variables, data types, data structures, loops and conditional statements.

Also, in the last part of the course, you will learn some advanced concepts  such as reusing code using functions, classes, and modules.
